      "title": "Ask HN: Do you have an unusual income source",
      "content": {
        "text": "<div class=\"toptext\" style=\"margin-top:4px\">Most of use here are wage earners. I keep hearing of people making money with interesting side hustles. Like my neighbour rents graduation gowns for the local university. I'd love to find something like that but I need inspiration.</div>",
