        "id": "19b8b4cfd14d9fe9e99b7cf3510d9eef",
        "source_id": "48632914",
        "content": {
          "text": "Let me tell you something that does not make money: selling fiction books as an independent author (through physical copies, Kindle ebooks and Kindle Unlimited). Family member is a good writer, has been trying to \"make it\" for a few years already (published multiple books, has good reviews), and the monthly profit is still not enough to buy a pizza. reply",
