        "id": "3718dbb546c289b8dc4438e4cb2b1c24",
        "source_id": "48631876",
        "content": {
          "text": "I teach some music private lessons and play jazz gigs. An easy side hustle that should require not more than 10 years of work for a couple of hours a day to qualify if you apply yourself. You could be a hundredaire! :-) \"Jazz Musician\": someone who puts a $10000 horn in a $1000 car to play a $100 gig reply",
